Just use leetcode math pattern to do the math. Leetcode math pattern works this way.

1. Convert question into equation.
2. Do one of following :-
2.1 Invert the equation (if greater then smaller)
2.2 Rearrange equations (move left or right) 
2.3 Simplify the equation by adding brackets.

# Approach

here, use math pattern this way :-

```(mean)*(n+m) = sum(m) + sum(n)```

